{"tid":1242982,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"獨居老人家選票被操控？","createTime":"2019-06-19T09:22:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T11:15:25.000Z","uid":260715,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5c0d578ada8f6dd1125839f027645942b84fde19","tid":1242982,"uid":260715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:22:28.000Z","msg":"屋企有老人家係公屋獨居<br />\n今日特登打電話問佢有冇登記選民<br />\n點知老人家話從來冇登記過選民 但每次選舉都會收到一封信話自動選左某某人<br />\n我上選舉事務處個網check老人家已經登記左做選民<br />\n<br />\n唔知老人家有冇理解錯封信（可能係謝票信？果d標題&ldquo;謝謝各位支持之類&rdquo;）<br />\n因為唔係住公屋，所以唔清楚公屋咩玩法<br />\n會唔會係唔知咩情況下老人家傻下傻下登記左投左票都唔知？<br />\n不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7accb2a4fd03519647c788fc8d975af10eec5d6","tid":1242982,"uid":134801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:25:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c09f593dbc8effb3613ba210743c27887123fa9e","tid":1242982,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:25:51.000Z","msg":"建制係咁<br />\nD配票靚到好似用計數機咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1cc6379504d320384f498e6487ab9282d9ed6f","tid":1242982,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T09:32:56.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推"},{"pid":"da5123aff1bca9df728b4bccca8f7f096d593796","tid":1242982,"uid":235727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:05:31.000Z","msg":"係咪填咗啲以為有jackso攞嘅form，唔知道係選民form"},{"pid":"d3f83522b65bc7f498808e1f0232c05890883f18","tid":1242982,"uid":105598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:12:38.000Z","msg":"有得自動投票咩？"},{"pid":"cb74ef27c717a59ecb32867fd62350151cf4b71a","tid":1242982,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:14:38.000Z","msg":"一封信話自動選左某某人<br />\n冇呢封信好難做野, 或者會唔會係佢拎某啲機構派嘅社區福利時簽左啲乜野"},{"pid":"443a91b48345ee365ccef0abb993ebe3d6b07f99","tid":1242982,"uid":252311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB